data.description: Rehabbed top floor 2 bed 1 bath condo surrounded by a beautiful courtyard and many other amenities. 2 story Condo which gives you more of a townhome feel; walk into spacious living and dining room with lots of sunshine and attached balcony overlooking greenery. kitchen with granite counter top, stainless steel appliances and beautiful cabinets and remodeled bathroom. Spacious bedroom with closets on the upper floor and living and dining and kitchen on the main level. Enjoy the park with playground and tennis court within walking distance. Low HOA includes heat, water and gas. Laundry in building and includes one parking spot and storage.
